text: He was as lame as a duck. He had lost a leg and most of his face skin in a tragic collision with a boat propeller.
What did The Wind say to the Indian? "Kill them all!" The Indian was Schizophrenic and killed three tribesmen before being subdued.
Give a man a fish and you feed him for breakfast; he spends the rest of the day hungry.
A horse walks into a bar, both the horse and its rider are promptly disqualified from the event. They place dead last.
How do you kill two birds with one stone? You cage two birds and beat each in turn with the same stone.
Why did the doctor leave his practice? It was 4:00PM and office hours are 9-4.
A priest, a minister and a rabbi get on an elevator. Later; a priest, a minister and a rabbi get off the elevator.
What do you get when you cross a hippo and a rhino? Two angry animals.
Why did the little girl fall off the swing? She did not have good Motor coordination.

Knock knock!

The sound a woodpecker makes.
Perkins serves "breakfast at any time". I ordered Pancakes in the year 2250.

What did the Pope get for Christmas? 

Presents.
A man walks into a bar. He is rushed to the hospital and treated for injuries.
A plumber and a construction worker walk into a bar. The bar is successfully repaired and re-opens the following Monday.
That kid has got a good head on his shoulders. He lost his neck in a tragic accident.
